"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-world-1927123-panic-paris-olympics-cause-huge\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Hospitals inParisare reeling under the strict new security systems that have been put in place for the2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access to the medical centres in areas of the capital close to sporting venues have become fraught with difficulty, potentially endangering people's lives.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Security has been stepped up in preparation for the beginning of the sporting festival, that starts on Friday 26th July.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The city has been divided into red and grey zones, which require special permits and passes to enter.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aegean_dispute\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.4772766609270228e-13, \"text\": \"grey zones\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aegean_dispute\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aegean_dispute\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Nightmare for Macron as Paris Olympics in 'crisis' after new strikes announced    While the fences and roadblocks are making life difficult for ordinary Parisians, medical professionals are facing a nightmare.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An ambulance driver complained that it was taking much more time to pick up and drop off patients, many of whom require urgent treatment.\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It takes 50 minutes to 1 hour to make a journey to drop off or pick up a patient, and that's a problem because the man we are picking up has been there waiting for 2.5 hours,\\\" he told the channel BFMTV.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do what we can, but it's hard to get around,\\\" he added despairingly.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities have introduced a Game Pass with a QR code for people who need to enter the security zones.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Anne arrives in Paris ahead of 2024 Olympics after Zara misses out on spot  Do not miss:Paris Olympics chaos as half a million tickets still unsold ahead of Games  Do not miss:Paris Olympics fear 'major threat' from Russia just days before Games  Two perimeters have been set up to secure the competition venues and the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999990498054, \"rank\": 9.502009238228192e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1314, \"end\": 1318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zara_Carmichael\", \"score\": 0.8910107579552592, \"rank\": 0.09618526463275909, \"text\": \"Zara\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zara_Carmichael\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zara_Carmichael\"}, {\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9997882377345578, \"rank\": 0.00010739232372641697, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first is the red zone: located near the competition venues, it is accessible to pedestrians and cyclists without a Games Pass.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Only vehicles require a pass to enter.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The grey zone, on the other hand, is closed to pedestrians, cyclists and vehicles from 18 July to 1pm on 26 July.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To enter, people must have the Games Pass QR code.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A man recovering from heart surgery was forced to take the metro rather than.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A taxi to get back home, due to the access difficulties.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His wife told BTMTV: \\\"The hospital secretary told us to take the metro.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ideally, we'd like to find a taxi, but she said that would be complicated, so I am trying to find out because the metro seems too complicated.\\\"\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Excitement is growing in France's capital as the clock ticks down on the Opening Ceremony.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9948520466353895, \"rank\": 0.004712183243877406, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Paris 2024 will mark the first time in history of the Olympic Summer Games that the official opening is held outside a stadium.\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of familiar images of athletes marching out along an athletics track, guests and viewers will be treated to a colourful river parade through the heart of the French capital.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2925, \"end\": 2931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9933641153629893, \"rank\": 0.0033725932720634444, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2942